message:
Report: Pair tortured human trafficking victim in front of children at Pineville, N.C. hotels. " The victim has been very brave in coming forward and we hope that if there are more victims out there, then they too will be inspired to come forward.”
#lawenforcement #endhumantrafficking #northcarolina
